.NET Framework 3.5.name: OVRRaycaster
.NET Framework 3.5.summary: Extension of GraphicRaycaster to support ray casting with world space rays instead of just screen-space pointer positions

fields.name: m_RaycastResults
fields.summary: For the given ray, find graphics on this canvas which it intersects and are not blocked by other world objects

fields.name: s_SortedGraphics
fields.summary: Perform a raycast into the screen and collect all graphics underneath it.
